{
  "texts": [
    "Each data observation is linked directly to a clinical concept and a visit, enriching it with valuable metadata, thus aligning with the researchers' \"minimum requirement\" approach for metadata entry.",
    "27 Our choice to integrate HL7, particularly HL7/JSON, into our SQLite database improves functionality and adherence to FAIR principles.",
    "This globally recognized standard ensures seamless data exchange with other systems, facilitating efficient data sharing and collaboration.",
    "32 The HL7/JSON integration also enhances data accessibility, allowing data to be easily parsed across platforms and applications due to its human-readable format.",
    "Our SQLite database system offers a structured storage system for diverse clinical data types, enabling efficient search and filtering."
  ]
}